headline: Allegion Schedules Webcast to Announce 2025 Fourth-Quarter, Full-Year Results
summary: DUBLIN, February 05, 2026--Allegion plc (NYSE: ALLE), a leading global security products and solutions provider, will release its 2025 fourth-quarter and full-year financial results on Tuesday, Feb. 17, before the market opens.
